{"tid":1676970,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"砌機求救","createTime":"2019-10-26T18:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T04:17:23.000Z","uid":38911,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"60026f024cf36822fd196ecef7bba94b5b7c9ff2","tid":1676970,"uid":38911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:42:55.000Z","msg":"我尋日新砌左部機 成功入到Bios<br />\n跟住因為太夜所以就收工瞓覺<br />\n當時係火牛底板CPU RAM M2 SSD Display Card 同 AIO都砌左落去<br />\n今日起身就無開過機就砌埋幾隻舊嘅SSD同HDD落去<br />\n點知開唔到機 唔知乜事<br />\n無畫面 CPU紅色LED長著 十秒八秒後就會Reboot<br />\n但都係無畫面 CPU 紅色LED長著 KEEP係咁LOOP<br />\nRAM的RGB燈係著嘅<br />\n拔左Display Card 都一樣<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSpec.<br />\nIntel i9 9900k<br />\nGigabyte Aorus Z390 Master Ver.1<br />\nKingston Hyper X Fury RGB 3466Mhz 16GB x 2<br />\nGigabyte Aorus GeForce RTX2080Ti Xtreme Waterforce 11G<br />\nWesten Digital SN750 500GB M2 SSD<br />\nPhanteks Revolt X 1200W<br />\n<br />\n救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6a0e25c690ee3e8b539b78fc9673225149bc0b","tid":1676970,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:43:18.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"174825f3b744e1c7c3d3e553f740fed19f38ff68","tid":1676970,"uid":54777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:10:43.000Z","msg":"有冇全新hdd or ssd?<br />\n有就淨係連新<br />\n啲舊嘅唔好砌落去住"},{"pid":"0e5950adb218a0ab5b722ff7826e0ae31a2958e5","tid":1676970,"uid":38911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T0